OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThe night will then remain largely dry
OL,8,Fwith clear spells. A mild night with
OL,9,Fgentle winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA largely dry day with bright
OL,12,Fspells. Cloud will thicken at times in
OL,13,Fthe west to bring the odd spot of
OL,14,Frain. Remaining warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,17,Fcloudy on Monday but otherwise dry
OL,18,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Remaining
OL,19,Fquite warm for most but becoming
OL,20,Fcooler along the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
